apps.description:
Kaver is a poster of unusual events and places not for everyone. Stay tuned!

See the poster of unusual places and offline-events of Budapest. 
A poster of the world's top and unique online events is also available.

Be the first to learn about unique places and events that you cannot find by yourself

Kaver is:
- events from all over the world;
- events not on other poster;
- map with unusual and hidden places;
- exhibitions of modern art  (online and in person)
- online performances from theaters around the world;
- conterts of underground bands;
- the craziest live broadcasts!

Kaver is not only standard theaters, concerts and exhibitions, but also unique content that is not like anything else. Most of the events and broadcasts are not on other posters!

Find:
With the help of search and filters, you will quickly find exactly those events that you want to see and visit.
And if you don't want to search, just press the button and watch random broadcasts.
Or see the events in the selections for all occasions.

Choose:
Become an expert in the world of events, surprise your friends!
Unusual performances, the most daring and modern exhibitions, creative and poetry evenings, concerts of indie musicians, private parties, cool festivals, and of course the coolest, unusual, amazing places in the city. Take your pick and go!

Home recreation can be varied! We offer you an alternative to films and serials: theater performances of the world, concerts of your favorite or little-known bands, free training, exhibitions of modern or classical art, parties, parties, DJ sets and much more! Everything is at your disposal.
Arrange online home parties, concerts, walks around the cities of the world! Your possibilities are endless.

What you can do in the Kaver app:
- watch the poster of the most top-notch and unusual events;
- watch broadcasts directly in the application;
- customize filters for interests;
- find out about the availability of tickets, their cost;
- buy an e-ticket,

Explore unique worlds! Secret locations and special events unlock only via subscription.- never miss events of interest! The application will remind you of events from the poster.




Install Kaver, be trendy!

